        <h2>Incorporating Age and Chronology</h2>
        <p>It is medically vital to comprehend that the Devine Formula is rigid—it entirely ignores biological aging. As humans cross into their senior years, maintaining slightly more mass is frequently linked to better bone density and survival rates against illness. Always cross-reference rigid numerical frameworks alongside your true chronological reality using an <a href="/calculator/age-calculator">Age Calculator</a> to secure nuanced medical advice.</p>
        
